The paper proposes a method for federated learning that involves local representation learning on each device to learn useful and compact features from raw data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and multimedia (cs.MM).
